data.enText: a serious illness affecting one or both lungs that makes breathing difficult

simple_means.memory_skill: pneumon 肺 + ia 某种病 → 肺炎

tr: respiratory disease characterized by inflammation of the lung parenchyma (excluding the bronchi) with congestion caused by viruses or bacteria or irritants

value.def: Pneumonia is a serious disease which affects your lungs and makes it difficult for you to breathe.
